Forum 84 Low 'White Crew Green'
results.story: The adidas Forum 84 Low ‘White Crew Green’ offers a simple two-tone colorway of the retro hoops shoe, featuring legacy details that include the adjustable ankle strap and X-shaped overlay. A subtle Cloud White finish is executed on the leather upper, accented with hairy suede three-stripes in a lush green hue. A more subdued shade of olive green is applied to the sneaker’s terry lining and rubber outsole. The latter supports an off-white rubber midsole, fitted with an EVA wedge that’s exposed on the medial side.

4D Fusio 'Grey Solar Yellow'
results.story: The adidas 4D Fusio ‘Grey Solar Yellow’ applies a gradient finish to the sneaker’s 3D-printed midsole, partially concealed by a protective TPU wrap and formed using an innovative process that blends light, oxygen and liquid resin. The lattice structure supports an upper crafted from breathable Primeknit in a monochromatic grey finish. The form-fitting, sock-like build is enhanced with an integrated lacing system that incorporates translucent tubing for a futuristic aesthetic.

results.name: Wales Bonner x Nizza Low 'Cream White Scarlet'
4D Fusio 'Screaming Orange'
results.story: The adidas 4D Fusio ‘Screaming Orange’ features a form-fitting Primeknit upper in a blend of fiery hues. An elastic collar accentuates the sock-like fit, while perforated detailing enhances the sneaker’s breathability. Decorative translucent tubing is integrated into the laces for a futuristic aesthetic. Finely tuned cushioning is provided by adidas’ revolutionary 3D-printed midsole, wrapped in a semi-translucent TPU cage for added stability and support.

results.name: Toy Story x Stan Smith Big Kid 'Rex The Dinosaur'
NMD_R1 'Crew Navy'
results.story: The adidas NMD_R1 ‘Crew Navy’ makes use of an engineered mesh upper in a one-note finish. Perforated quarter panels are accented with tonal three-stripes, while a molded heel patch features an embossed Trefoil logo. A webbing pull tab at the heel is marked with text that reads ‘The Brand With the Three Stripes.’ Responsive cushioning comes courtesy of a full-length Boost midsole, fitted with black EVA plugs and supported by a matching black rubber outsole.

NMD_R1 'Black Screaming Orange'
results.story: The adidas NMD_R1 ‘Black Screaming Orange’ updates the lifestyle runner with a neutral palette enlivened by vibrant pops of color. The form-fitting knit textile upper is treated to a sleek black finish with a series of no-sew overlays in charcoal grey. A contrasting fluorescent orange hue is applied to the sneaker’s signature three-stripes and color-blocked Boost midsole, featuring blocky EVA plugs in keeping with the classic NMD aesthetic.

NMD_R1 V2 'Black Speckled'
results.story: The adidas NMD_R1 V2 'Black Speckled' spotlights the sneaker’s full-length Boost midsole, which is finished in metallic blue and purple tones and dusted with tiny white speckles. Midsole plugs are rendered in black, matching a breathable knit upper made with 50% recycled content and zero virgin polyester. Contrasting white branding hits include an adidas Trefoil on the tongue tag and ‘The Brand With the Three Stripes’ printed in multilingual text on the lateral quarter panel.

results.name: NMD_R1 V2 'White Speckled'
results.story: The adidas NMD_R1 V2 ‘White Speckled’ carries a sock-like knit upper designed to wrap around the foot in lightweight, breathable support. The stark white coloring up top is offset by a full-length Boost midsole, featuring textured sidewalls covered in speckled detailing and a gradient metallic finish that transitions from blue to purple. The sneaker’s rear midsole plugs extend up to form a supportive heel cage, connected by a webbing strap marked with text that reads ‘The Brand with the Three Stripes.’

results.name: 4D Fusio 'Black Orange Pink'
results.story: The adidas 4D Fusio ‘Black Orange Pink’ spotlights the shoe’s groundbreaking 3D-printed midsole, created using an innovative process called Digital Light Synthesis. The lattice structure is reinforced with a smoky TPU wrap and finished in a gradient blend of pink and orange, contrasting colors that reappear throughout the predominantly black Primeknit upper. The futuristic tooling is accentuated with the addition of translucent tubes that form the sneaker’s eyelets and pull tab.

Wmns Stan Smith 'Doodle'
results.story: The adidas women’s Stan Smith ‘Doodle’ carries a synthetic leather upper that incorporates Primegreen, made from high-performance recycled materials that constitute 50% of the sneaker’s build. The pristine white finish is enlivened by a series of colorful graphics bunched around the heel, each rendered in a hand-drawn, DIY look. They’re joined by traditional branding elements that include perforated three-stripes and a stamped Stan Smith tongue label in a subtle peach hue.

results.name: The Muppets x Stan Smith Little Kid 'Kermit The Frog'
4D Fusio 'Black Ultra Purple'
results.story: The adidas 4D Fusio ‘Black Ultra Purple’ treats the sneaker’s Primeknit textile upper with a color-fade effect that transitions from white to dark grey. A similar gradient design is applied to the TPU cage that wraps around the midsole, featuring a violet around the heel and a contrasting pop of yellow at the toe. The fluid finish is offset by a stark black 4D midsole, rendered in a data-informed lattice structure that’s created by blending light, oxygen and liquid resin.

results.name: NMD_R1 'Cream White Screaming Orange'
results.story: The adidas NMD_R1 ‘Cream White Screaming Orange’ showcases a monochromatic finish that complements the lifestyle runner’s minimalist build. A subdued shade of ivory suffuses the engineered mesh upper, accented with tonal three-stripes on the perforated quarter panel. The lightweight build is placed atop a crisp white Boost midsole, featuring bright orange EVA plugs affixed to the lateral sidewall. A similar shade of orange is applied to the durable rubber outsole.

results.name: Marvel x Stan Smith 'I Am Groot'
NMD_R1 'White Crew Navy'
results.story: The adidas NMD_R1 ‘White Crew Navy’ rides on a standard full-length Boost midsole, featuring color-blocked sidewalls in white and navy. EVA plugs maintain the classic NMD look while adding stability to the sneaker’s plush ride. Up top, white knit textile is designed to hug the foot for a snug, sock-like fit. adidas Trefoil branding decorates the molded heel patch and woven tongue tag, while signature three-stripes are rendered in a contrasting navy hue.

adidas Continental 80 END German Engineering Cream
results.story: The END. x adidas Continental 80 ‘German Engineering’ takes inspiration from the golden age of motorsport, featuring a premium build that nods to iconic German sports cars. Specifically, the ‘60s and ‘70s color catalogs of BMW and Porsche inform this pair’s aesthetic, featuring a cream-colored leather and suede upper with multicolor three-stripes. Mismatched adidas and END. branding lands on each shoe’s heel tab and tongue, while the lateral heel displays ‘Made in Germany’ text and the sneaker’s numbered edition, which is capped at 500 pairs.

results.name: adidas Continental 80 END German Engineering White
results.story: Limited to 500 pairs, the END. x adidas Continental 80 ‘German Engineering’ pays tribute to German technical ingenuity in the field of motorsport. The UK-based retailer dresses the retro silhouette in a white tumbled leather upper, featuring multi-colored three-stripes that nod to iconic race car liveries associated with BMW M Sport and the Martini Racing Porsche. Mismatched adidas and END. branding is applied to each tongue and heel tab, while the lateral heel is stamped with ‘Made in Germany’ and the sneaker’s numbered edition.

adidas Yeezy 700 V3 Kyanite
results.story: The adidas Yeezy 700 V3 ‘Kyanite’ showcases flowing stripes of blue coloring throughout the breathable upper, constructed from monofilament engineered mesh with exoskeletal RPU overlays coated in a glow-in-the-dark finish. Interior bootie construction delivers a snug fit, while a reinforced rubber toe cap provides added durability. The sneaker rides on a lightweight EVA midsole encapsulated in an off-white PU cage, supported by a herringbone rubber outsole.

results.name: adidas GT Paris SNS
results.story: Releasing as part of the Swedish retailer’s ‘Hometown Love’ series, the Sneakersnstuff x adidas GT ‘Paris’ features a familiar color scheme that pays homage to the City of Lights. The upper is constructed from ivory-colored suede with tonal leather three-stripes, a blue molded tongue and a red leather heel tab stamped with an adidas Trefoil. Additional adidas branding appears on a custom sockliner printed with a map of Paris. The low-profile silhouette rides on a semi-translucent gum rubber cupsole.

results.name: Wmns Adilette Comfort Slide 'Legacy Purple'
results.story: The adidas women’s Adilette Comfort Slide ‘Legacy Purple’ updates the cushy sandal with an injected EVA midsole in a subtle violet hue. Step-in comfort is provided by the combination of a contoured footbed and a wide single-bandage upper, lined in quick-drying textile and marked with a repeating adidas logo. Underfoot, a durable synthetic outsole features a crisp white finish and a diamond traction pattern for reliable grip.

results.name: adidas ZX 2K Phormar Craig Green White
results.story: The Craig Green x adidas ZX 2K Phormar ‘White’ combines the British fashion designer’s progressive sensibilities with adidas ZX running technology. One piece of semi-translucent white nylon is utilized on the upper, featuring high-density tension cords running through stitched channels outlining the collar, heel and throat. A drawcord lacing system works in tandem with an interior sleeve to provide a secure fit. Responsive cushioning comes courtesy of a partially wrapped Boost midsole, reinforced underfoot by a translucent rubber outsole.

results.name: Predator Accelerator FG 'Royal Blue Solar Yellow'
results.story: The adidas Predator Accelerator FG ‘Royal Blue Solar Yellow’ delivers an updated version of the shoe’s namesake model from 1998. Like its antecedent, the low-top is constructed from stitched K-leather with a traditional fold-over tongue, off-center lacing and rubber elements throughout the strike zone. Underfoot, the updated split Controlframe outsole is borrowed from the Predator Freak+, featuring studded traction designed for firm-ground surfaces.

results.name: Adizero Spark MD J 'Royal Blue'
results.story: The adidas Adizero Spark MD J ‘Royal Blue’ delivers a lightweight two-tone football cleat built for little kids. The streamlined upper is constructed from coated Sprintskin, emblazoned with three-stripe branding on the lateral toe. Breathable mesh is utilized on the padded collar and tongue. A low-profile Bounce midsole is supported by a molded Quickframe outsole, featuring an aggressive lug pattern for stop-and-go traction.

results.name: Adizero 11 Primeknit 'White Black'
results.story: The adidas Adizero 11 Primeknit ‘White Black’ outfits the performance football cleat in a breathable white knit upper, fortified with a durable TPU overlay and accented with contrasting black three-stripe branding. Dual webbing pull tabs and an elastic ankle cuff allow for easy on and off, while an integrated lacing system produces a feeling of lock-down. The seamless build is supported by a lightweight Sprintframe outsole, equipped with a series of Sprintstuds that deliver turf-digging traction through every play.

results.name: Superstar J 'Pink Iridescent'
results.story: Built for little kids, the adidas Superstar J ‘Pink Iridescent’ updates the shell-toed sneaker icon with an eye-catching finish. The pink leather upper is accented with serrated white leather three-stripes and multicolor iridescent paneling on the sneaker’s lateral side. A similar iridescent finish is applied to adidas branding hits on the tongue and heel tab. The low-top is mounted on a durable rubber cupsole, complete with a herringbone traction pattern underfoot.
